name: Utopia, (shopping center)
directions:
It a square building with a lot of entrances. It’s named Utopia and made out of a lot of glass. When you’re inside, go to the middle of the mall and on to the second floor. Up there will be a display of different departures for busses. And next to that is the restrooms. 

If you don’t find it search for “Espresso house” and then if you look around you’ll find it.

Good luck!

It is free and (sadly) divided in genders, but there’s also a handicap restroom. 
(There’s stalls in both the male and the female one)
